data.description: Welcome to this charming home in Arlington, TX! This well-maintained gem offers a cozy and comfortable living experience. The spacious backyard is a true delight, boasting a fantastic outdoor kitchen, perfect for entertaining family and friends. This home has been lovingly cared for and exudes a timeless charm. The wood-burning fireplace creates a warm and inviting atmosphere, perfect for those cozy evenings. This home also provides a sunroom that would be great for a closed off den or a working space! Situated on a generous lot, this property provides ample space for outdoor activities and gardening enthusiasts. Enjoy the convenience of quick access to major highways, making commuting a breeze. Minutes from 360 & I-20. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this wonderful Arlington residence your new home!
